b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2219,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Adding the Mana Spiral to More Adventurers! [Addendum]","message":"<div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1623304800\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><br>In a data update around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1624168800\\"><\/span>, the adventurer AI for Summer Verica will be changed so that she uses the Everlasting Summer Lv. 4 skill as soon as its skill gauge is filled.&quot;<\/div><hr><div>A sixth mana circle, the mana spiral, will be added to certain adventurer starting <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1622181600\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The adventurer affected this time and her stats are described below.<\/div><div>Note: Unlocking an eligible adventurer&#39;s mana spiral requires special materials specific to that adventurer that can be earned from the daily bonus of the Trials of the Mighty quest.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Affected Adventurers<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Summer Verica (shadow\/staff)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Stats<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fb5\\u2605 adventurer<\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp adjust\\">\\n<div class=\\"thumbList\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"thumbnail\\">\\n\\t\\t<img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/9ef1e0ca46417b44b14854af4a21d0a62.png\\">\\n\\t\\t<img class=\\"rarity\\" src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/23b8fc2cd656aa0d5ef96984f257ce7e2.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"discription\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"charaName\\">Summer Verica<\/div><\/div>\\n<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>100<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li><li class=\\"type\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/1fc4080420e16a67744809f28590c98b2.png\\"><\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"skill\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>10<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>964<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>563<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"total\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>3,227<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t<\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt class=\\"skill-cost-wrap\\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/19c706c3440276a68b516e5597e4e0c32.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Everlasting Summer<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"skill-cost\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Shareable<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"txt-num\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>6<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Restores HP to all allies, removes blindness,<br>and continues gradually healing over time.<br>Also, increases the entire team\'s strength,<br>grants all teammates a shield, and grants<br>them overdamage.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Recovery Potency: 44<br>Skill Energy Required: 5,916<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 18,753<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbBlindness Relief<br>\\u30fbStrength +8%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 60 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br>\\u30fbShield<br>\\u3000\\u3000Charges: 1<br>\\u3000\\u3000Potency: 30% of max HP<br>\\u30fbOverdamage<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 30 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Potency: 50%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br>\\u30fbHP Regen<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Potency: 35<br><\/div><\/dd><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a716da6beae4f87ab2ee2be17fa868172.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Moment of Passion<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Grants all teammates a buff that restores HP<br>relative to the amount of damage they inflict,<br>and grants the user a strength amp. After this<br>amp is granted, this skill will not grant it again<br>for 30 seconds.<br>The skill gauge for this skill can be filled by<br>attacking enemies, but when the skill gauge for<br>Everlasting Summer is not at 100%, this skill\'s<br>gauge will also gradually fill automatically.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Skill Energy Required: (Fills Automatically)<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbHP Drain<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 30 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Potency: 5%<br>Amps:<br>\\u30fbStrength Amp (Team Amp MAX Lv. = 2)<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/799d30d618475a89802dad3d29b6ca252.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Recovery Potency +20%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIncreases the potency of recovery skills by 20%.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Shadow) HP 60% = Strength +6%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Shadow: <br>increases their strength by 6% when<br>their HP is 60% or above.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/2c1b0769c70b1a55ec5c1156121748af2.png\\"><\/span><span>Beach Beauty<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Fills 100% of skill gauges at the start of quests,<br>and, when HP is full, increases strength by 15%<br>and the potency of recovery skills by 25%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/accaa8252fc4f8f52a5bf0964aac9cf32.png\\"><\/span><span>Potent Blindness Res +100%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to blindness by 100%.<br>When the user is hit by an attack that would have<br>blinded them, their strength is increased by 15%<br>for 10 seconds. After activating, this buff will not<br>activate again for 15 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/799d30d618475a89802dad3d29b6ca252.png\\"><\/span><span>Recovery Potency +15%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Increases the potency of recovery skills by 15%.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.<\/div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1622095200,"prev_article_id":"2237","next_article_id":"2238","image_path":"","update_time":1623379437}}}'